-- Lehman has spoken to financial buyers for investment businesss
-- 
-- Wed Sep 10, 2008 10:07am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/09/10/lehman-ceo-idUSMAR04442720080910

 

 Sept 10  (Reuters) - Lehman Brothers Holdings CEO says has spoken to strategic, financial investors for investment
   management business   

 * CEO says since Q2, was "significant additional deterioration" in credit
   markets
 * CEO says intense public scrutiny was a distraction to clients,
   counterparties, employees
 * CEO says spun off entity will use held to maturity accounting
 * CEO says remains committed to examining all strategic alternatives to
   maximize shareholder value
 * CEO says "we're on the right track to put these last two quarters behind US"